data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. MOTIVATED SELLER . . . . .Beautiful 4 bedroom 2 ½ bath concrete block home on 6.55 acres with bonus room! This home features an open concept living area with a wood burning fireplace. Spacious master with large walk-in closet, three additional bedrooms with a shared bathroom, all complete with new carpet. The large bonus room has a ½ bath and is the location of the laundry area, complete with an exterior door. This room can be used as a 5th bedroom, home office, playroom etc. The kitchen has a formal dining area with sliding glass doors that lead directly outside to the fully fenced yard with a loquat tree and banana trees. The entire home has new interior and exterior paint, NEW ROOF (2023), 4-year-old water heater. Two small sheds in the yard for storage of tools and equipment. A large boomerang shaped pond is located on the property. NO HOA, NO CDD & NO DEED RESTRICTIONS! Plenty of room for all your hobbies - horses, chickens, RV parking, ATV riding, ETC! This property provides privacy and seclusion while still having easy access to local amenities. Within minutes of the lovely town of San Antonio, Publix, shopping centers- The Grove at Wesley Chapel, Tampa Premium Outlets, dining options, public schools, medical facilities, entertainment venues & more! Come check out this bright, clean, move-in ready home.
